{"tid":2063714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明日是誰的死忌？","createTime":"2020-06-14T08:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T09:02:53.000Z","uid":199893,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2c61173afa6adee58637a637c6d2d4aa2014d2","tid":2063714,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:37:56.000Z","msg":"是在太古廣場穿著黃色雨衣墜樓身亡的烈士&mdash;&mdash;梁凌杰的死忌<br />\n他的死亦印證了制度的死 香港的死<br />\n<br />\n還請香港人勿忘梁烈士的精神<br />\n惡法確實已被撤回 但人命無法像法例一樣彈出彈入<br />\n梁烈士嘅死 係香港政府所造成 港府不容抵賴<br />\n<br />\n送中條例已被撤回 但仍有惡歌法 國安法的挑戰<br />\n這場革命未停 不能停 亦不可以退縮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rphcbOz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrphcbOz.png&h=9717c8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不要妥協 不要讓步呀香港人"},{"pid":"92460dfc21784723c69277fb481cc9f74ab9edcf","tid":2063714,"uid":104431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd64b292e796e153852bbc85aabb0d5a84326e4","tid":2063714,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"若然我們今天退縮<br />\n哪怕是退一步 還是兩步<br />\n明天是梁烈士的死忌<br />\n後天會是你我的死忌<br />\n大後天......<br />\n從始會是香港人的忌年<br />\n也許只有四年一次的四月廿九安可歇息"},{"pid":"24b98b4062113418ac1120999ce53aea04699563","tid":2063714,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"呀！不，就連田月廿九都係八三一的悼念"},{"pid":"be81a5b84dc060240af693edc718d341dccb02be","tid":2063714,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:43:00.000Z","msg":"去贈一朵白花<br />\n繫上一絲白絲帶"},{"pid":"8d9cb7218246a94f29b78de2f21e9c168e9724d9","tid":2063714,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"[615黑衣白絲帶] 民陣呼籲615全港黑衣、佩戴白絲帶，悼念梁凌杰逝世一周年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2062874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2062874</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"544b2d8b99671c48473ee692ceb3b8a28d4b08df","tid":2063714,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:44:21.000Z","msg":"梁凌杰呢個名 作為香港人 係一定要記得"},{"pid":"308b418b4d00a9ba6c6e2a8759a830a346f74eb7","tid":2063714,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"544b2d8b99671c48473ee692ceb3b8a28d4b08df","tid":2063714,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:44:21.000Z","msg":"梁凌杰呢個名 作為香港人 係一定要記得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cc30bba059709e4cb4f9e18af90dc5a0b9c4c8","tid":2063714,"uid":143031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZR4Nmw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZR4Nmw.jpg&h=b27f93ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準備好白絲帶未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有絲帶用絲帶，冇絲帶用紙條<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">615黑衫白絲</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"f86069bc8e5bb42bb4feb0fd3e62d874276d8919","tid":2063714,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21cc30bba059709e4cb4f9e18af90dc5a0b9c4c8","tid":2063714,"uid":143031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZR4Nmw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZR4Nmw.jpg&h=b27f93ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準備好白絲帶未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有絲帶用絲帶，冇絲帶用紙條<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">